PRIVACY POLICY MBit Music™
cares about your privacy. Respecting your privacy is a fundamental policy of
MBit Music™
, and therefore, we formulate this Privacy Policy to inform you of how we collect, use and share your personal information.
Mbit Musi
c built the
Lock Screen Drawing
an Ad Supported app. This
SERVICE
is provided by
Mbit Music
at no cost and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding my policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use my Service.
BY USING THE PLATFORMS, YOU PROMISE US THAT YOU HAVE READ, UNDERSTAND AND AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY
.
Generally, we do not collect any PII from you when you download our Android applications. To be specific, we do not require the consumers to get registered before downloading the application, nor do we keep track of the consumers' visits of our application, we even don't have a Server to store such PII.
Non- Personal Information
We may collect and use non-personal information in the following circumstances. To have a better understanding in user’s behavior, solve problems in products and services, improve our products, services and advertising, we may collect non-personal information such as installed application name and package name, the data of install, frequency of use, country, equipment and channel.
If non-personal information is combined with personal information, we treat the combined information as personal information for the purposes of this Privacy Policy.
Information we get from your use of our services
- Device information - Device-specific information such as your hardware model and operating system version.
- Unique application numbers - Certain services include a unique application number. This number and information about your installation (for example, the operating system type and application version number)
- Anonymous identifiers - we use anonymous identifiers when you interact with services such as advertising services and others.
Permissions uses in App and its uses:
Permissions:
INTERNET:
This permission is required to access the internet and
to display a message if your device is not connected to the internet.
This permission is also required for certain functionalities of Firebase, which we use to provide some features within the app
CAMERA:
This permission is only used in the Join Friends Room to allow you to scan a QR code to join a friend's room.
Additional Notes for Android 13 (API level 33 and above):
READ_MEDIA_IMAGES/READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE:
This permission allows us to access your photo library so you can choose an image as the background for your drawing.
Android 13 introduces scoped storage, where apps can access specific folders chosen by the user instead of the entire storage.
READ_WALLPAPER_INTERNAL :
This permission is used to access your device's lock or home screen wallpaper and display it within the Drawing Together when lock screen drawing is enabled.
SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW :-
This permission is necessary to display the drawing activity over other apps on the screen.  This is required for the core functionality of the app when using features like lock screen drawing.
WAKE_LOCK :-
This permission allows the app to detect when your device wakes up from sleep. This is needed to display the Drawing Together on the lock screen if lock screen drawing is enabled.
